Gino Piserchio https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gino_Piserchio 0 Eugene "Gino" Piserchio (September 5, 1944 – March 22, 1989) was an American actor, composer and musician. Piserchio was noted for being an accomplished musician. He was one of the first musicians to master the Moog synthesizer.
